\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\fs32 Kide2 editor - Help guide
\par \cf2\fs22 A tool for developing Kitto2 applications
\par \cf3\f1\{keepn\}\cf2 
\par \f0 Welcome to Kide2 editor Help guide
\par \cf0\b0\f2\fs20 KIDE2 is a free tool to ease and speed up the development of Kitto2 applications. 
\par In this IDE you can use GUI wizards, automatic syntax checking and verification, database reverse engineering, special advanced editors, and so on.
\par 
\par \cf3\b\f0\fs22\{bmc KideLogo.jpg\}\cf2 
\par 
\par What is Kitto2?
\par \b0\fs20 Kitto2  is a development tool to create data-driven RIAs (Rich Internet Applications) withAjax features and a MVC structure. Project files are written using the Yaml notation, while the engine is fully developed in Delphi by Ethea and is fully extensible. Applications created with Kitto2 work with all databases supported by Delphi through ADO, DBExpress or FireDAC. The user interface is made with the ExtJS 6.2 library.
\par Visit \cf1\strike ethea.it/eng_kitto.asp\cf3\strike0\f3\{link=*! ExecFile("http://ethea.it/eng_kitto.asp")\}\cf2\f0  to find more information about Kitto2.
\par \b\fs22 
\par Open Source
\par \b0\fs20 Kitto2 and Kide2 are Open-Source and free! They are released under \cf1\strike\f3 Apache.org License 2.0\cf3\strike0\{link=*! ExecFile("http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0")\}\cf2\f0 
\par \b\fs22 
\par First Use\cf0\b0\f2\fs20 
\par To learn how the program works, read the Kide2 \cf4\strike user's guide\cf3\strike0\{linkID=110\}\cf0  section.
\par 
\par \cf2\b\f0\fs22 System Requirements
\par \b0\fs20 the program is compatible with all of 32-bit Windows versions. It requires only 30MB of disk space.
\par \cf0\f2 
\par \cf2\b\f1\fs22 COPYRIGHT
\par \cf3\{bmc Ethea_300x9\f0 8\f1 .\f0 gif\f1\}\cf2 
\par \cf0\b0\f2\fs20 Kitto2 and Kide2 editor are \cf1\strike\f0 Ethea's\cf3\strike0\f3\{link=*! ExecFile("http://www.\f4 ethea.it\f3 ")\}\cf0\f2  products.\cf2\b\f1\fs22 
\par }
